---
title: Paneer and Spinach Curry with Basmati Rice
description: Tonight, we’re bringing you our healthy version of the traditional 'saag paneer' curry which pairs delicious Indian cheese (paneer) with spinach and spices. We're opting for heart-healthy olive oil instead of the traditional ghee (clarified butter) for a guilt-free dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/paneer-and-spinach-curry-4fef386e.jpg
